<title>Jeff Bezos</title>
<media id="ch13media08" alt="A photo shows Jeff Bezos flashing the slide showing the phenomenal growth of Amazon’s Kindle eBook sales in comparison to physical book sales during his presentation of the new Kindles."><image mime-type="image/jpg" src="../../media/Bezos.jpg"/></media>
